reviews: Good back up solution. I use it for storing video files etc that don't need fast and regular access too. These have become very cheap over the years as ssd have became mainstream.
Good reliable storage. I have trusted SanDisk for years now.

Fit is good. Great design.
Many people ask about and comment on the shirt.

Holds lots of gear etc. Seems to be durable enough for daily use and will be good enough for casual camper or hiker.

Only con for price is that the straps loosen up in shoulder over time... Not to much.... But if you like to sinch tight and keep it that way this doesn't hold.

Affordable casual hike/camp pack or for someone going to school or work etc.

Stitched edges are great. The underside of the mousepad has rubbery steel series logos to minimize the pad from moving around the desk/table. Mouse glide and tracking are great. The size medium is perfect for me. Not too big and not too small.
Bought as additional storage for my Samsung Galaxy S10. Speeds are as advertised.

Great addition to my Razer Huntsmen Tournament Edition keyboard. I used two to six o-rings per key. Some keys had 1 or 3 stems, I used 2 o-rings per stem.
Number of rings needed for your board and preference will vary.

Don't expect a dramatic sound difference. It is quiter but not by huge degree. The feel is a more noticeable difference. You get slightly less travel and a nice cushion when bottoming out. Overall my board is quiter and feels alot better to me.

I would have given 5 stars but almost all keys have a plastic tab piece on them from molding process. You can see in first pic if you look at keys close up. The keys are amazing otherwise though.

I bought these for my razer huntsmen tournament edition. I didn't replace all keys, kept using F1 through f12 as well as space bar from original razer set. I wanted to keep the function key legends and didn't want the hyper x logo on spacebar.

Great under desk headset holder.
3m adhesive holds great! I added this to a new desk I bought and it sticks on and holds no problem. I let it stick for 48 hours before leaving a headset attached. Make sure surface is clean if just relying in 3m adhesive. If you are worried about holding strength there are two holes in headset holder so you can screw it to desk for permanent hold.

Nice sleek and durable case.
Hard back is nice and helps case keep clean while offering dual layer protection. Raised front helps protect screen of phone.
Buttons feel great. All cut outs are precise.
Dropped phone shortly after putting this on and held up great :)

Sound is decent for price. Connectivity is great, no issues with my Galaxy S10.
Using one earbud at a time works perfectly. This was key for me cause I use the mainly at work and keep one bud in at a time.
Nice pump but I wish it would stay closed with out the need of being attached to mount bracket.

I am very pleased with the desk. It was very easy to put together. Took all of 6 minutes.
The desktop itself is of high quality for the price. The legs are very sturdy when all assembled. Doesn't move or wobble at all. Supports my monitor and PC etc no problem.

Reviewed just over a month after purchase.

Chair didn't come with instructions to out together, this could be a problem for some... It was simple enough FOR ME to put together though... Took 20 minutes.

The wheels could be alot better. Mine make a metal sound when rolling and don't roll well at all.

Chair makes a popping noise when getting up or sitting down or adjusting. Not always but often. It is the air/gas mechanism.

Chair doesn't stay at set height long. Eventually the chair will just randomly decompress and air pushes out and you go down..

I wouldn't recommend buying this chair.
It is usable but there are surely better chairs around same price on market.
Doesn't work in landscape mode. When in landscape mode phone becomes loose from vibrations/bumps while mountain biking. The phone stays secure in portrait mode.

Bought this for biking. It is compact and doesn't take much room in my backpack so I keep it in there at all times.
Fits over other layers.

Good grip. They also help reduce vibrations. No movement in grips thanks to double lock on. The plastic end caps are great too, if the end cap were metal matching with the metal locks would've been a nice touch. Cheaper that I could find at local store WHEN they were in stock.
Fit is as expected. Lots of boxers for money. Mesh flap vent on crotch is good feature.

Perfect fit!
Well made. Great for casual or work wear.
Tluv shirts are great. Good quality. Fit is good and they are comfortable.
Tluv shirts are great. Good quality. Fit is good and they are comfortable. NASA retro design is my favorite.
Well made. They look great!
Perfect fit. The pants have some stretch, are comfortable and durable. Will be ordering these regularly.
Looks great. Fit is perfect. Great hoodie.

review_title: Looks good but fits a little larger than expected.
reviews:
Looks great and is soft. The hood is nice.
Fits a little bigger than I'm used to for a medium.

I was very impressed at first with these speakers... I took them out of box and set them up on my desk. After listening to them for an hour or so I took the speaker grills off to look at the speakers and seen that the right side dome on the woofer is pushed in... This had to have happened during packaging as they come shipped with grills on and I never removed when setting up.
I don't notice any difference in sound... But how am I to know as they came damaged so I have no reference for proper sound. Sound is good I guess... I am just not happy they came damaged like that. Not sure if it effects sound or not.
Good blank shirts. Fit is good. Gildan shirts have always been good for me.
Durable and comfortable.
Good fit and keeps you dryer/cooler than a normal t-shirt. Not sure about how long they can last as I order new blank shirts all the time but these are great. Gildan makes good value shirts.

I ordered 1 pair to try these out and I liked them so I ordered 2 more in different colors/shades.

They are a good price, fit well and are very comfortable.
